  "detailed_description": "Whizz Ball is a high speed cross between Pong, Breakout and Pinball.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n*** PLEASE NOTE ***<br />\r\nThe use of a controller is highly recommended. The keyboard and mouse can be used in single player games only.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlay single player against the computer or with up to 4 friends locally.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCustomise your experience with only the options you want in the game. Make it steady and simple or fast and frantic.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDefend your blocks and redirect the ball towards your opponents.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUse after touch and take control of the ball.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPowerups and powerdowns affect your bat or the ball.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nScore points to restore lost blocks.",
  "about_the_game": "Whizz Ball is a high speed cross between Pong, Breakout and Pinball.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n*** PLEASE NOTE ***<br />\r\nThe use of a controller is highly recommended. The keyboard and mouse can be used in single player games only.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlay single player against the computer or with up to 4 friends locally.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCustomise your experience with only the options you want in the game. Make it steady and simple or fast and frantic.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDefend your blocks and redirect the ball towards your opponents.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUse after touch and take control of the ball.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPowerups and powerdowns affect your bat or the ball.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nScore points to restore lost blocks.",
